edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery

Class DiscoveryService

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.service.BaseService
      • edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery.DiscoveryService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseServiceInterface, DiscoveryServiceInterface

    public class DiscoveryService
extends BaseService
implements DiscoveryServiceInterface
    The discovery service holds the list of discovery's that are running in the system. The status of all discoveries is mentioned as well. The discovery service will also start any discoveries that were active when the server was shut down and need to complete.
